data.description: Adorable year round lake house at Big Lake! If you’re looking for affordable lake living with lake access, look no further! Home has a designated pier that’s just a short walk down the street and to your left. Big lake is a ski lake with 1-4 ski hours. Home has beautiful curb appeal with a new front deck addition that adds so much charm, along with a small fenced in yard. Inside the home offers a cozy open floor plan, one bedroom and one full bath on the main level, a second bedroom and full bathroom upstairs, and a huge loft that could be used for a third bedroom, office, playroom, or second living space. Updates to the home include: new fencing in the backyard, vinyl flooring, painted kitchen cabinets, new paint throughout, new dishwasher (2 months old), & new microwave (2 months old). Lastly, home has an oversized garage large enough for 2 cars and a boat. Be sure to check out this wonderful home!
